item.description:
Genre: Electronic, R&B, Jazz, Pop
Style: Smooth Jazz, Downtempo, Vocal
Year: 1993
Source: DVD

"Life Promise Pride Love" is a DVD album by English band Sade, released in 1993. It features R&B artist Sade in each stage of her career. The title takes one word from each of Sade’s multi-platinum albums and spanning four albums.

Helen Folasade Adu, better known as Sade, contributed her unique music style to the 1980s music world. She created a new sound by fusing smooth jazz with R&B and soul.
